---
title: Burger & Chicken Sandwich Bar with Super Sauce, Dill Pickles, Umami Mayo & Slaw
description: Super sauce, umami mayo, or both? Slaw on top or on the side? Skip the pickles or double up? Everything is more delicious when you get to choose. Customize your cookout with these deluxe build-your-own burgers and chicken sandwiches, complete with gouda cheese, sliced tomato, grilled onion, and a creamy slaw. For sauces, choose between umami mayo, homemade super sauce, or both! Friends can have it their way, you can have it your way, and everyone can be together. That’s the beauty of assembling your own!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burger-chicken-sandwich-bar-37fe97ef.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/burger-chicken-sandwich-bar-6255a31c3c39130625191934-c93c5f2c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/burger-chicken-sandwich-bar-6255a31c3c39130625191934
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: North America
course: main course
author: Sara Heilman
nutrition:
  calories: 1560 kcal
